                <br>
                <h2>What kind of work can I get done?</h2><br>                
                <p>Anything that can be done on a computer – from web and mobile programming to graphic design – can be done on Upwork. Our freelance experts can master a range of projects:<p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Tiny or daunting</li>
                    <li>Short or ongoing</li>
                    <li>Team-based or individual</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Whether you need a writer to knock out a 500-word blog post or a full-fledged software development team to support your business, our tools and the expert freelancers in our marketplace can accommodate you, lucky boy!<p>
