    <div id="hiring" class="container-fluid blueContainer">
        <br><br><br><br><br>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-6">
                <img src="/images/hiring.png" alt="Hiring" height="400">
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6 text-left">
                <br>
                <h2>How do I hire the right freelancer?</h2><br> 
                <p>Start by writing a clear and concise job post. Each freelancer submits a cover letter and link to their Upwork profile covering:<p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Portfolios, skills and experience</li>
                    <li>Client feedback</li>
                    <li>Language and communication proficiency</li>
                </ul>
                <p>You'll get applications from independent professionals and receive our personalized recommendations within minutes. From there, just interview your strongest candidates and hire your favorite.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <br><br>
        <a href="#specialbackground">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-up"></span>
        </a>
        <br><br>    
    </div>

    <!-- Container (Payments Section) -->
