        <br><br><br><br><br>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-6 text-left">
                <br>
                <h2>How do payments work?</h2><br>
                <p>Pay your freelancer per hour or per project, whichever you choose. For hourly projects, the freelancer bills you once a week, and we'll send a secure payment to your freelancer. For fixed-price projects, we'll release funds to your freelancer after they meet pre-set milestones. In either case, you're covered by FreheLantser Payment Protection, assuring that you only pay for work you approve.</p>
                <p>All payments go through our secure system. Choose from the following billing methods:<p>
                <ul>
                    <li>American Express</li>
                    <li>Mastercard</li>
                    <li>PayPal</li>
                    <li>Visa</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-6">
